==English==
===Etymology 1===
Latin suffix [[-aster]], meaning '[[little]]', '[[petty]]', '[[partial]]', '[[incomplete]]'.

===Suffix===
'''-aster'''
#Used to form diminutive and pejorative nouns, labeling someone pretending to be what they are not.

